OL,3,CBirkenhead shortlisted as UK's first
OL,4,CTown of Culture
OL,6,FBirkenhead has been shortlisted to
OL,7,Fbecome the UK's first Town of Culture.
OL,9,FThe winner will receive #3 million
OL,10,Ffrom the government and will host a
OL,11,Fseason of culture in 2028.
OL,13,FThe competition's run by run by the
OL,14,FDepartment for Culture, Media and
OL,15,FSport and aims to retore pride in
OL,16,Flocal areas in every part of Britain.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
