OL,3,CBirkenhead shortlisted as UK's first
OL,4,CTown of Culture
OL,6,FThe 15 towns shortlisted will now
OL,7,Freceive #60,000 each to develop their
OL,8,Fbids which will be assessed by judges
OL,9,Fwith the winner announced early next
OL,10,Fyear.
OL,12,FAmong the towns Birkenhead will be
OL,13,Fcompeting against are Great Yarmouth,
OL,14,FPort Talbot and Strabane.
OL,16,FPrevious winners of the UK's City of
OL,17,FCulture were Derry-Londonderry 2013,
OL,18,FHull in 2017, Coventry in 2021 and
OL,19,FBradford in 2025.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
