OL,3,CBirkenhead shortlisted as UK's first
OL,4,CTown of Culture
OL,6,FCulture Secretary Lisa Nandy said:
OL,7,F"The fact that we received so many
OL,8,Fapplications just goes to show how
OL,9,Fproud people are of their towns."
OL,11,FThe judging panel was chaired by
OL,12,FBrookside creator Sir Phil Redmond.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
