OL,3,CBirkenhead shortlisted as UK's first
OL,4,CTown of Culture
OL,6,FHe said: "The response to the
OL,7,Fcompetition has been, to say the
OL,8,Fleast, overwhelming, quite literally
OL,9,Ffrom all four corners of the UK. It
OL,10,Fhas been fantastic that nearly 400
OL,11,Ftowns have come forward, sharing their
OL,12,Fsense of pride, ambition and desire to
OL,13,Fdemonstrate how much they have, and
OL,14,Fcontinue to contribute to our national
OL,15,Fstory."
